mental health <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">consultants</ENAMEX> and primary care providers<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">.46</NUMEX>-<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">48</NUMEX> A
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">collaborative</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT_DESC">model</ENAMEX> using emergency department <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">physicians</ENAMEX> to screen
and mental health <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">professionals</ENAMEX> to perform the intervention is the
approach that is most likely to be widely adopted<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">.49</NUMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">Alcohol</ENAMEX> use among emergency department <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> is not likely a
