free to maintain their own insurance codes. They may either adopt
the models intact, modify them to meet their specific needs, or
ignore them. Emergency <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">physicians</ENAMEX> should provide their legislative
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">representatives</ENAMEX> and insurance <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">regulators</ENAMEX> with information about how
